# waves/ — R.A.E.H. wave artifacts

## Protocol
1. **DRAFT** — Author (orchestrator) + **wave-spec**: INTENT → SPEC.xml → PLAN.xml  
2. **REVIEW*** — Reviewer stamps `REVIEW-STAMP.md` (same session, max 5 rounds)  
3. **AGREE** — `AGREED: YES` + `acceptance.hash`  
4. **EXECUTE** — only after stamp YES  
5. **VERIFY** — optional F-04  
6. **HANDOFF** — orchestrator updates STATUS/MEMORY; append SESSION_HANDOFF

## Layout
```
waves/
├── README.md
├── _template/
│   ├── REVIEW-STAMP.md
│   ├── EXEC-REPORT.md
│   └── STATUS.md
└── <YYYY-MM-DD>-<slug>/
    ├── SPEC.xml
    ├── PLAN.xml
    ├── acceptance.hash
    ├── REVIEW-STAMP.md
    ├── EXEC-REPORT.md
    └── STATUS.md
```

**Authority:** stamp file on disk. Chat AGREED does not count.
